        <p>Privy vs ActiveCampaign: scenario 1 — B2B cart below MOQ threshold. At $133 AOV and 38% margin, full-price recovery contributes $50.54 vs $43.46 after a 14% code (Δ $7.08). Ladder touch 1 favors SMS urgency; watch for recovery for fully OOS cart. Email 1 ~75m, email 2 ~45h, SMS branch ~7h for opted-in only.</p>
