        <p>Privy vs ActiveCampaign: scenario 3 — international shipping quote sticker shock. At $133 AOV and 38% margin, full-price recovery contributes $50.54 vs $43.46 after a 14% code (Δ $7.08). Ladder touch 3 favors no-discount assist; watch for welcome discount stacking with cart code. Email 1 ~75m, email 2 ~45h, SMS branch ~7h for opted-in only.</p>
